1.8
log
@Multi-cpu support for top.  Each cpu now gets its own stats line.
Based on work by todd@@ at the hackathon.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: utils.h,v 1.7 2004/10/07 06:26:12 otto Exp $	*/

